      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Khalid, from usman Bin Isa, from Talha Bin Zayd, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Eating the clay inherits the hypocrisy’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn Khalid from ‘Uthman ibn ‘Isa from Talhah ibn Zayd who has said the following: “Abu ’Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ’Eating clay is of the sources of hypocrisy.”’ "
        ]
      }
